      • Sid

        public Sid​(byte[] sidBytes)
        Parses a SID object from a byte array.
        Parameters:
        sidBytes - SID structure encoded as bytes
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if sidBytes is null
        IllegalArgumentException - if sidBytes contains less than 12 bytes
        IllegalArgumentException - if SID's revision is not 1
        IllegalArgumentException - if SID's subauthority count is more than 15
